                            <comment id="43914" author="niu" created="Tue, 28 Aug 2012 22:48:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/3806&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/3806&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="43913" author="niu" created="Tue, 28 Aug 2012 22:44:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think we should set the QUOTA_AUTO as 0 for such interop tests, I&apos;ll change the t-f to check lustre version before enabling the jobstats.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
